        </div>
        <div class="space-y-6 reveal" style="--delay: 2;">
          <span class="text-[12px] font-semibold text-[#1E3A5F] uppercase tracking-widest">About Us</span>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-display font-bold text-[#1E3A5F]">
            신뢰와 혁신으로<br>20년의 역사
