          </div>
          <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-[#1E3A5F] text-lg mb-3">인재 솔루션</h3>
          <p class="text-[#2D3748]/60 text-sm leading-relaxed">채용 컨설팅, 인재 교육, 조직 문화 혁신까지 인적 자원의 가치를 극대화합니다.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="reveal bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-xl p-8 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-[#1E3A5F]/5 transition-all duration-500 group" style="--delay: 4;">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-[#1E3A5F]/5 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-[#1E3A5F] transition-colors duration-500">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-[#1E3A5F] group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M3.055 11H5a2 2 0 012 2v1a2 2 0 002 2 2 2 0 012 2v2.945M8 3.935V5.5A2.5 2.5 0 0010.5 8h.5a2 2 0 012 2 2 2 0 104 0 2 2 0 012-2h1.064M15 20.488V18a2 2 0 012-2h3.064M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-[#1E3A5F] text-lg mb-3">글로벌 진출</h3>
          <p class="text-[#2D3748]/60 text-sm leading-relaxed">해외 시장 조사, 현지 법인 설립, 파트너십 구축 등 글로벌 비즈니스를 지원합니다.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Performance / Numbers -->
